# Emacs cheat sheet

C = ctrl
M = alt
+ = same time
- = do together

A YCMd on the top status bar indicates the buffer is in ycmd major mode.

C-x customize-themes		-- choose color theme
C-x C-c				-- exit emacs
C-c Y v				-- show debug info
C-c Y V				-- show version
C-x 0				-- close a window
C-x o				-- switch window
C-x <left>			-- switch buffer, keep pressing left until you see the ycmd traceback errors
C-x <right>			-- switch buffer, keep pressing right until you see the ycmd traceback errors
C-x C-s				-- save
C-x k				-- kill buffer in same window

Using C-x C-v should report:
Server is running
